title: KMFDM - Rules [1996] EAC FLAC  LOG
description:
KMFDM - Rules [1996] EAC FLAC LOG

Rules is a KMFDM single from their 1996 album Xtort. Rules includes remixes of three tracks from Xtort; the title track "Rules" as well as "Inane" and "Son of a Gun".

Track listing

   1. "Son of a Gun (Overhauled by Sascha K. & Chris Shepard)" 3:41
   2. "Inane (Undermined by En Esch & Chris M. Flam)" 8:28
   3. "Rules (Reapplied by Raymond Watts & Steve White)" 8:13
